metadata.name: When he woke
metadata.description:
It was also during that time that he met the young Shen Xue.



She was gentle and beautiful, but bold and hot.



Despite his repeated rejections, she persisted and later said it was love at first sight.



He was lonely since childhood, years of blood and fire, never had that warmth, he slowly sank into it.



After they got together, they had a quiet time.
